{"name":"兰彻斯特战斗损耗模型","description":"经典兰彻斯特方程 - 红蓝双方兵力对抗与消耗动态","engine":"SIMULATION_PACKAGE","simulation":{"algorithm":"RK4","time_start":0,"time_length":30,"time_step":0.1,"time_units":"DAYS"},"elements":[{"type":"STOCK","name":"RedForce","behavior":{"initial_value":5000,"non_negative":true},"display":{"coordinates":[150,250],"size":[130,50]}},{"type":"STOCK","name":"BlueForce","behavior":{"initial_value":4000,"non_negative":true},"display":{"coordinates":[550,250],"size":[130,50]}},{"type":"VARIABLE","name":"RedFirepower","behavior":{"value":"0.015"},"display":{"coordinates":[350,80],"size":[120,50]}},{"type":"VARIABLE","name":"BlueFirepower","behavior":{"value":"0.012"},"display":{"coordinates":[350,420],"size":[120,50]}},{"type":"VARIABLE","name":"RedReinforce","behavior":{"value":"50"},"display":{"coordinates":[50,120],"size":[110,50]}},{"type":"VARIABLE","name":"BlueReinforce","behavior":{"value":"30"},"display":{"coordinates":[650,120],"size":[110,50]}},{"type":"VARIABLE","name":"RedMorale","behavior":{"value":"1 - 0.00005 * (5000 - [RedForce]) * (5000 - [RedForce])"},"display":{"coordinates":[50,380],"size":[110,50]}},{"type":"VARIABLE","name":"BlueMorale","behavior":{"value":"1 - 0.00005 * (4000 - [BlueForce]) * (4000 - [BlueForce])"},"display":{"coordinates":[650,380],"size":[110,50]}},{"type":"FLOW","name":"RedLoss","from":"RedForce","to":null,"behavior":{"value":"[BlueForce] * [BlueFirepower] * [BlueMorale]","non_negative":true},"display":{"from_coordinates":[150,275],"to_coordinates":[50,350]}},{"type":"FLOW","name":"BlueLoss","from":"BlueForce","to":null,"behavior":{"value":"[RedForce] * [RedFirepower] * [RedMorale]","non_negative":true},"display":{"from_coordinates":[550,275],"to_coordinates":[700,350]}},{"type":"FLOW","name":"RedReplenish","from":null,"to":"RedForce","behavior":{"value":"ifthenelse([RedForce] > 100, [RedReinforce], 0)","non_negative":true},"display":{"from_coordinates":[50,250],"to_coordinates":[150,250]}},{"type":"FLOW","name":"BlueR